name: Harajuku Body Painting
description:
Trompe l'oeil harajuku body painting. Trompe l'oeil is the art of making a painting look real.

Fashion is everything, and harajuku fashion is all about color!

I sometimes like to make something impossible when I paint faux clothing. In this case, her stockings seem to blend into her skin.

Originally gifted to the top holders of the Diver objkt #192068

model: Alison Little
body paint and photography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
